BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14
15
SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
15
16
codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
16
17
This act shall be known and may be cited as the “Racing Facility
17
18
and Racetrack Nuisance Immunity Act”.
18
19
SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19
20
in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1.2 of Title 50, unless there is
20
21
created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21
22
A. As used in this section, “racing facility” means a
22
23
designated area where competitive vehicle and motorsport races are
23
24
conducted including, but not limited to, the track, spectator areas,
24
